- `apps/extension/src/popup/services/textToSpeech.ts` — Reusable TTS service with `speakText`, `stopSpeaking`, `isSpeaking` and callback support (`onStart`, `onEnd`, `onError`), extracted from duplicated inline code
- `apps/extension/src/popup/components/WordDetails.tsx` — Full word detail view displaying: meaning, Vietnamese meaning, pronunciation, part of speech, difficulty, status, topic, example sentence, synonyms, antonyms, word family, collocations, source sentence, personal note, tags, source page, and created/updated timestamps. Includes pronounce button with visual playing state

**Modified:**
- `apps/extension/src/popup/components/SavedWordsView.tsx`
  - Vocabulary items are now clickable — clicking opens `WordDetails` with the full `ExtensionVocabEntry` loaded from IndexedDB
  - Fallback to a partial entry if not found in IndexedDB (graceful degradation)
  - Keyboard accessible (`Enter`/`Space` triggers detail view, `role="button"`, `tabIndex={0}`)
  - Uses shared `speakText` service instead of inline TTS
  - Hover highlight on vocabulary items

**Validation:** TypeScript compiles cleanly (no new errors), all 116 existing tests pass.
